// This program reads a listing of Pilots & Passengers For the first six Virgin Galactic flights to space, from a text file
// generated by the first part of ths program.
// Then displays the information in a GUI. Along with a Space ship that follows the mouse.
// CSC1301 MW 10-12. CRN:4340
// Project3_AdamAdkins_Part1
// Author: Adam Adkins
